### Создать пользователя (outbox → Kafka → email) — как save-order.http в kafka-order-service
POST https://localhost:8443/api/users
Authorization: Basic admin admin123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kafka Demo User",
  "email": "kafka-demo@example.com",
  "age": 30
}

### Проверить Mailpit
GET http://localhost:8025/api/v1/messages
